{"tid":2285702,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"炒左個油麵","createTime":"2020-11-14T10:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T14:09:07.000Z","uid":239860,"like":29,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e59682cf859dd1891ec756a43ffc23e367b3de4a","tid":2285702,"uid":239860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:23:20.000Z","msg":"好似好耐冇出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為我真係好懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見冇咩點出炒粉麵，於是今次整左黑椒雞肉炒油麵，好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣可以睇下條片<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ptrq43BVGsI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPtrq43BVGsI&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=4c7bc878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ptrq43BVGsI</a><br />\n製成品 切左啲蛋絲同芝麻上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hH4oH2E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhH4oH2E.jpg&h=35606b0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n切完啲料就將啲料炒一炒先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7jE4suw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7jE4suw.jpg&h=9ea53e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後炒埋一堆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vHfWiBj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvHfWiBj.jpg&h=aacab7ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有興趣就訂閱埋我個Facebook 同ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFb: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/captopuskitchen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcaptopuskitchen%2F&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=a13f3e32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/captopuskitchen/</a><br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CGaAioqJrXL/?igshid=17jre4m7bfvma\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.c